description:
Enjoy some time off and adventure during Zuzalu on Jet Skis!

Feel free to walk-in without RSVPing whenever you have some time to relax. Though reserving a slot will ensure no waiting time.


We're launching from Marina Beach - https://goo.gl/maps/RTcseLEmiPBfYMgPA?coh=178572&entry=tt


Bring 50 euro for 30 minutes of fun, in cash or Revolut, to cover the rental and fuel costs.

Check out "Jet Skis (14.05)" topic to reserve a slot.
